2abd85bf68cd5f32e4f3db1f85a2edf7d511","tid":1849082,"uid":248290,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSn0yuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSn0yuC.jpg&h=eab1e7ad&s={SIZE}\" /> 維尼 先係 病毒源頭"},{"pid":"d873cf5997853def65ccd70c2be20febca8db584","tid":1849082,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"上次都老屈文在寅話香港事務純屬中国內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec8308f701ee8c7cf6a71a6d90245a131317019","tid":1849082,"uid":102982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"On撚柒鳩"},{"pid":"c0904193f7bc03807ea8ffb12996d3a1c56515ed","tid":1849082,"uid":108674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"683d82fc4a3c9b878bd77f536bcb91053f35dd54","tid":1849082,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/huanjing/jt-01282020122829.html/0128x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fhuanjing%2Fjt-01282020122829.html%2F0128x.jpg&h=8f6c7d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國家主席習近平在北京會見世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞，習近平指中國政府以公開透明的態度及時向國內外發布新型肺炎疫情的訊息，積極回應各方關切，歡迎世衛參與是次疫情防控工作。又指在中共領導下充份發展中國特色社會主義制度的優勢，精準施策，有信心、有能力打贏這場仗。<br />\n<br />\n習近平就指：「對中國人民來說我們現在正進行一場嚴肅的鬥爭，中國政府是高度重視，因為政府的宗旨是把人民的生命安全、身體健康放在最高位之上，所以這一次的疫情防控工作，我一直是親自指揮、親自部署，我相信只有我們堅定信心、同舟共濟，科學防治、精準施策，我們一定會戰勝這一次的疫情。」<br />\n<br />\n央視及新華社報道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">譚德塞會面時表示世衛和國際社會高度讚賞並充分肯定，中國政府採取的果斷措施，感謝中方為阻止疫情蔓延所做的巨大努力，又指中方的行動之快、規模之大實屬罕見，展現出<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國效率，值得借鑒</span>。</span></span>其他報道指世衛不主張撤僑，在當前形勢下應保持鎮定，沒有必要過度反應，世衛組織對中國政府防控疫情的能力充滿信心。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，中共中央印發《關於加強黨的領導為打贏疫情防控阻擊戰提供堅強政治保證的通知》，要求各級黨委激勵引導黨員、幹部在疫情防控鬥爭中挺身而出、英勇奮鬥，對表現突出的要表揚表彰，對不敢擔當、作風飄浮甚至弄虛作假、失職瀆職的要嚴肅問責，要組織黨員、幹部做好群眾工作，穩定情緒，不信謠、不傳謠，堅決打贏疫情防控阻擊戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/122551610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F122551610&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=9dfcc8df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F122551610&h=e4318d22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/122551610</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"個世界終有一日會俾啲離地撚害死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea9f8600e0a7b50a0164b46e7cf5e0f4e9a0e3e","tid":1849082,"uid":280752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦...中共世衛..."},{"pid":"143cfb7644a59e391432cfcb5d9b580c5bc56d2c","tid":1849082,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:41:38.000Z","msg":"奶共世衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef9138f4ae9a4b21d349723d6a1f60889269196","tid":1849082,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:49:54.000Z","msg":"行賄確定"},{"pid":"9cc3a9834ff690e025d71a78d26780610039a49e","tid":1849082,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:53:16.000Z","msg":"幾喼美金送上機喇，如果唔係點會請到條世廢過去疫國送死喎。"},{"pid":"126f48b364bad498c9f2c3cef7099093095a1c88","tid":1849082,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"繼續讚佢就岩<br />\n讚下讚下讚到佢支暴再一刀桶埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53abb898f6307e879bbca41b168ffd200a430929","tid":1849082,"uid":149306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:53:38.000Z","msg":"撤緊僑㗎仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾大都讚住佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif