315915b8a8062e5a193ce02a7a59e270c7a","tid":1849082,"uid":183758,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:42:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾死廢柴支那死肥狗魔鬼平<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXy7cQB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXy7cQB.png&h=07e53804&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/90929452cf6ebc798c39523f5495333f/tenor.gif?itemid=14207653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F90929452cf6ebc798c39523f5495333f%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D14207653&h=aa9fe856&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7016292c2bad00a82697d7e7457dae0c6857dd0","tid":1849082,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />世衛條契弟"},{"pid":"7ee68cdd0fd137ec3b42066aa7f3d7ce289691bc","tid":1849082,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2Em2Bw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2Em2Bw.jpg&h=565f5dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 基本上已可斷言武漢肺炎係來自武漢P4實驗室<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fnews.guo.offload.media%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25133703%2FBrief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=ab8338e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人包：<br />\n1. 武漢沙士病毒好可能係人工<br />\n<br />\n-佢同2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒嘅E protein 100% 一樣 (相應嘅DNA 相似度都有225/228)，下一隻最接近嘅病毒已經只有低於95%一樣。<br />\n<br />\n病毒嘅基因複制同人類唔同；佢哋冇糾錯機制，發生變異機率相當大。即使E protein為保守序列，病毒品種相對不易產生變異，自然界中仍然非常唔可能有兩種冠狀病毒嘅E protein 完全一樣。SARS唔同亞種嘅E protein都有少量差別。<br />\n<br />\n-ORF8 基因通常病毒品種之間分別好大，2017浙江嗰隻嘅ORF8 同其他冠狀病毒最多只有60%似，但係同武漢沙士就有94.21%一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦推算武漢沙士病毒入侵人體嘅方式與SARS異常接近<br />\n<br />\nSARS入侵人體第一步，係病毒嘅S protein 痴落人體嘅ACE2 受體. 武漢沙士嘅S protein 整體上同SARS或者2017浙江嗰隻都唔似，但係真正痴落人體嗰部分就同沙士好似。最重要嗰五個氨基酸雖然同沙士有四個唔一樣，但係物理特性相似。電腦分析亦估算武漢沙士同人體ACE2 receptor 親和度非常高，只比SARS略低<br />\n<br />\n所以文章推斷為：有可能係有人參考沙士入侵呼吸道細胞ACE2 受體嘅方法，去改造2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒，再放出自然環境（如武漢市場）繁殖一段短時間"},{"pid":"e5e57c711e46bceb0c69a8557ce182d6b5db97b2","tid":1849082,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:24:48.000Z","msg":"呢隻黑鬼一早被雜種收買咗啦，成個奴才見金主咁款，疫情擴散全球，身為世衛總幹事都仲笑到咁開心，真無恥。"},{"pid":"12e61b445180b11fd34ed75e83e9893bbf860da5","tid":1849082,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"呢個垃圾黑鬼去支那第一時間係去見外長同國家主席，而唔係去武漢同見班醫生了解疫情，跟住就讚賞公開透明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca64d39b16cd63f4a9847b9eadd5d9f5262b57a","tid":1849082,"uid":341974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcda76310679200d0af72b31fbd47f96857c0c03","tid":1849082,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"去轉武漢先再講啦"},{"pid":"4d0c505e2e92d9bac9e39f1b80821a302b2ef3ba","tid":1849082,"uid":316663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"啲小學生係鍾意人讚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"h